org.mort11.util

Interface Constants


  • public interface Constants
    Constants contains port numbers, and other values that are used in other areas of the project. This is declared as an interface since all field variables in interfaces are implicitly declared as public static final, so now you don't have to write public static final for every variable.
    Version:
    11/08/2018
    Author:
    Joshua Ciffer, Benny Mirisola
